## 12. Success Criteria

| Metric | Target |
|--------|--------|
| API response time (sync) | < 800ms p95 |
| CTS normalization | 100% Zod pass on all 4 fixture files |
| Dedup scoring | Correct decision on all test pair fixtures |
| All endpoint tests | Pass — all 19 endpoints |
| No hardcoded credentials | Zero instances in codebase |
| Tenant isolation | Every DB query includes tenant_id |
| Phase 1 integrations | All 4 live with passing tests |
| Static inventory sync | All 4 suppliers sync successfully, records in hub_static_inventory |
| Two-stage search | Stage 1 returns candidates < 30ms, full search < 800ms p95 |
| Offline dedup | hub_dedup_pairs populated after sync, decisions applied at search time |
| Prompt seeds | All 15 prompts in DB, trigger conditions working |
| Onboarding flow | End-to-end with mocked supplier and doc fetch |

